# 🎤 Talent

| Method | Endpoint        | Description           |
| ------ | --------------- | --------------------- |
| GET    | `/talents`      | Get all talents       |
| GET    | `/talents/{id}` | Get talent detail     |
| POST   | `/talents`      | Create talent profile |
| PUT    | `/talents/{id}` | Update talent         |
| DELETE | `/talents/{id}` | Delete talent (admin) |

