# 🔄 Main Flow

```
Talent Register/Login
        ↓
Create Talent Profile
        ↓
EO Create Event
        ↓
Talent Apply / EO Invite
        ↓
Application Accepted
        ↓
Booking Created
        ↓
Event Completed
        ↓
Review
```

